          <div class="srow" style="padding:10px 0"><code style="color:#a855f7;font-weight:600">.geç</code><span style="color:#94a3b8;margin-left:10px">Sıradaki şarkıya geçer</span></div>
          <div class="srow" style="padding:10px 0"><code style="color:#a855f7;font-weight:600">.ses</code><span style="color:#94a3b8;margin-left:10px">Ses seviyesini ayarlar (1-100)</span></div>
          <div class="srow" style="padding:10px 0"><code style="color:#a855f7;font-weight:600">.sıra</code><span style="color:#94a3b8;margin-left:10px">Çalma listesini gösterir</span></div>
